{"tid":1846244,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"香港政府都唔想理 琴日私了武漢生化武器事件","createTime":"2020-01-27T14:09:38.000Z","updateTime":"2020-01-27T14:39:02.000Z","uid":42246,"like":14,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":10,"replies":[{"pid":"0768ed0af1d04bba5c8759fd34ffdf6d111fb62b","tid":1846244,"uid":42246,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-01-27T14:09:38.000Z","msg":"暴徒於旺角襲擊市民<br />\n＊＊＊＊＊＊＊＊＊<br />\n電台及電視台當值宣布員注意：<br />\n<br />\n請盡快播出下列消息，並在適當時間重播：<br />\n <br />\n　　今日（一月二十六日）晚上九時許，有暴徒於旺角彌敦道和奶路臣街交界聚集叫囂，曾一度佔據馬路，破壞社會安寧和秩序；其間更有暴徒襲擊三名途經的市民，濫用私刑。<br />\n　　 <br />\n　　警方警告暴徒立即停止違法行為，並將採取執法行動。 <br />\n <br />\n完<br />\n2020年1月26日（星期日）<br />\n香港時間22時11分<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n屌 d強烈譴責 絕不容忍<br />\n去曬邊<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n很似是撚旦 叫大家停手啦 就算<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n落台啦林鄭 你搞到養育你既香港變成一去不返狀態<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"17a33b6f68afd54006a7a70b076a185d7ead9b4b","tid":1846244,"uid":117819,"like":7,"dislike":0,"score":7,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-01-27T14:10:36.000Z","msg":"叫你割都廢鳩事<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"8fb70b8a687d871c2b9c70311d697701f0eb3902","tid":1846244,"uid":42246,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"quote":{"pid":"17a33b6f68afd54006a7a70b076a185d7ead9b4b","tid":1846244,"uid":117819,"like":7,"dislike":0,"score":7,"citedBy":1,"rep